# Palindrome Checker 🔁

Checks whether a given string is a palindrome.

## Features
- Ignores case and non-alphanumeric characters
- Provides immediate feedback on the result

## Technologies
- Python

## What I learned
- String processing
- Regular expressions
- Logical comparisons

## Run the program
```bash
python palindrome_checker.py
